Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.56,0:00:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zanpakuto…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.36,0:00:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their shape and abilities are\Nbased on their Soul Reaper's soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.72,0:00:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soul Reapers gain power
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.92,0:00:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by learning their names\Nand synergizing with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.97,0:00:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are born with Soul Reapers\Nand die with Soul Reapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.88,0:00:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is what Zanpakuto are.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.44,0:02:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So running away is\Nall that's left for you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.80,0:02:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You disappear from\Nmy range of vision{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.96,0:02:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}to attack with projectile weapons…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.79,0:02:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're as rotten as you look!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.56,0:02:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rotten? What of it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.40,0:02:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Does it have anything\Nto do with life and death?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.73,0:02:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's not compatible with\Nmy way of fighting.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.90,0:02:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Like I care.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.81,0:02:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I am a Zanpakuto whose\Nsole aim is to take lives.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.88,0:02:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have no interest in\Nhow my master fights.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.89,0:02:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I always thought that\Nthe relationship between{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.86,0:02:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}a Zanpakuto and a Soul Reaper was\None of communication and synergy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.53,0:03:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't know about\Nother Zanpakuto!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.56,0:03:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm me. I cut down lives!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.02,0:03:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I thought that was our sole\Nagreement between you and me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.46,0:03:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I see.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.65,0:03:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then it's easy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.40,0:03:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you die and my Zanpakuto\Ndisappears, so be it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.77,0:03:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't like you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.73,0:03:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I just realized that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.08,0:03:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Fine with me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.33,0:03:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because the feeling is mutual.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.58,0:03:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You say the Sword Beasts are\Nattacking Rukon District?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.99,0:03:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.96,0:04:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like they've teamed up\Nand are going on a rampage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.91,0:04:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope the damage doesn't get\Nany worse than it already is…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.52,0:04:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.51,0:04:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.76,0:04:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speak of the devil…\NMust be a Sword Beast!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.81,0:04:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.51,0:04:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what it is…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.49,0:04:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.28,0:04:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hisagi…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.45,0:04:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– Isn't that your Zanpakuto?\N– Go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.82,0:04:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one he's after…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.44,0:04:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.72,0:04:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.79,0:04:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.35,0:04:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.23,0:04:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A surprise attack again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.68,0:04:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't give up, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.53,0:04:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.07,0:04:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but I'll do\Nwhatever it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.48,0:04:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until we settle our fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.48,0:04:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will pursue you\Nto the ends of the earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.00,0:05:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reap, Kazeshini.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.08,0:05:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on, Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.93,0:05:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't that Hisagi's Zanpakuto,\NKazeshini?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.63,0:05:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did it join the Sword Beasts?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.53,0:05:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not what happened…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.22,0:05:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hisagi's Zanpakuto…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.72,0:05:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazeshini, is unlike\Nthe other Zanpakuto.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.65,0:05:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems it continues\Nto act independently
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.71,0:05:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even after the Muramasa\Nincident was resolved.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.90,0:05:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazeshini is a Zanpakuto\Nthat reaps lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.75,0:05:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hisagi said that once\Nit targets someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.34,0:05:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it will keep pursuing its target,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.89,0:05:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even if that target\Nis its own master,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.35,0:05:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,until the fight is settled…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.99,0:05:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're saying it stakes\Nits own life to kill?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.51,0:05:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man…Hisagi sure has\Na difficult Zanpakuto…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.65,0:05:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.08,0:06:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As usual, you keep\Nrunning from my blade!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.62,0:06:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While you fight by hiding,\Nas usual…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.69,0:06:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like the way\Nyou always try to
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.72,0:06:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,pull a surprise attack on people!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.48,0:06:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care!\NMy goal is to reap your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.72,0:06:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's meaningless to debate\Nour methods just for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.24,0:06:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bakudo 62, Hyapporankan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.38,0:06:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.65,0:06:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what you were aiming\Nfor right from the start…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.77,0:06:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.02,0:06:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate,\Nuntil you attack me head-on,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.32,0:06:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no intention of\Nsettling our fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.24,0:06:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For crying out loud…\NAlways trying to be the hypocrite!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.80,0:06:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.83,0:06:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We agree then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.18,0:06:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I say the same thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.93,0:06:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate the way you fight…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.13,0:07:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.80,0:07:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Hisagi…are you done\Nwith your business?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.01,0:07:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, sort of…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.09,0:07:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.25,0:07:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.62,0:07:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the time we got here,\Nthey had already disappeared…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.00,0:07:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only way is to chase them down\Nbefore they do more damage…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.18,0:07:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You attacked\Nyour master again, I hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.18,0:07:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give us a break, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.24,0:07:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of your selfish actions,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.66,0:07:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Soul Reapers are\Nstarting to think that
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.98,0:07:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we're going to cause\Nmore trouble for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.74,0:07:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you insist on\Ntrying to kill you master?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.95,0:07:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're free of Muramasa's\Nmind control, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.54,0:07:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's none of\Nyour damn business…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.16,0:08:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,None of our business?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.56,0:08:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What you do is your business,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.37,0:08:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but stop making trouble\Nfor us in the process.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.53,0:08:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are Zanpakuto…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.00,0:08:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to isolate yourself,\Nwe won't stop you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.77,0:08:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we won't help you, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.20,0:08:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.06,0:08:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't have any intention\Nof looking after you guys, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.08,0:08:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's so gloomy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.74,0:08:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look who's talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.94,0:08:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Sword Beast!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.10,0:08:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Sword Beast is attacking!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.58,0:08:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.93,0:08:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.07,0:08:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fancy meeting you here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.42,0:08:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.50,0:08:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time to fight you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.50,0:09:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.75,0:09:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.62,0:09:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it that important to protect\Npeople you don't even know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.66,0:09:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lost him…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.28,0:09:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.03,0:09:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.34,0:09:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not him…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.32,0:09:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.19,0:09:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.10,0:09:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.92,0:09:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not one of us…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.51,0:09:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you one of\Nthe Soul Reaper's dogs?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.88,0:09:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Soul Reaper's dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.32,0:09:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop messing around!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.10,0:09:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.01,0:09:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're…not one of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.72,0:10:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lump me in with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.86,0:10:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please…look after the baby…\NI beg you…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.09,0:10:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.28,0:10:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.73,0:10:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not one of the Sword Beasts,\Nbut I'm still a Zanpakuto.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.43,0:10:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no interest in anything\Nbut reaping lives…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.17,0:10:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This kid's hands are going to\Nmake my blade rust…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.07,0:10:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.22,0:10:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.23,0:10:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.90,0:10:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.28,0:10:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over there, Iba!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.41,0:10:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't cry! Come on, don't cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.50,0:11:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I have no choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.50,0:11:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.82,0:11:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came this far\Nwithout killing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.60,0:11:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be grateful and just\Ngo disappear somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.22,0:11:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, you are such a pain…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.00,0:11:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.61,0:11:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you follow me this time,\NI'll get rid of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.02,0:11:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you like that…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.86,0:11:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait here for\Nsomeone to come get you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.26,0:11:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.98,0:12:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!\NWhat is that on your back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.82,0:12:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazeshini,\Nhe looks so good on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.74,0:12:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it…\NI'm going to kill you…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.41,0:12:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, kid…Laugh…\NI said laugh…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.86,0:12:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gloomy kid…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.50,0:12:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know I already said this,\Nbut look who's talking…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.19,0:12:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.35,0:12:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should've just\Nleft the kid somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.70,0:12:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.06,0:12:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how,\Nbut it just turned out this way…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.43,0:12:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyways, somebody take him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.66,0:12:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.21,0:12:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.74,0:12:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you were grateful that\Nwe wouldn't be helping you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.78,0:12:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, but that was…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.38,0:12:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck raising a kid!\NBye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.15,0:12:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait a minute…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.62,0:13:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.34,0:13:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's not right…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.63,0:13:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is this happening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.50,0:13:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Spiritual Pressure…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.47,0:13:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The lieutenants are\Non the move…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.70,0:13:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.86,0:13:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.94,0:13:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll cut yourself\Nif you touch that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.62,0:13:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.90,0:13:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said no!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.50,0:13:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay. Don't cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.15,0:13:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, this brat really\Ngets under my skin…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.27,0:13:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.11,0:13:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You must be kidding!\NYou're kidding me! No way…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.75,0:14:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, this really\Nmesses things up…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.98,0:14:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There they are…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.90,0:14:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what was that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.82,0:14:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.78,0:14:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! Don't fall asleep here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.85,0:14:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you heard, Hisagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.50,0:14:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.31,0:14:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Among the Zanpakuto,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.18,0:14:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's a rumor going\Naround about yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.50,0:14:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.58,0:15:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay right here…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.50,0:15:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.06,0:15:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just be quiet and\Nstay here for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.50,0:15:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.54,0:15:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.54,0:16:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.02,0:16:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, they sure take up\Na lot of time…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.26,0:16:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stubborn bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.46,0:16:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.09,0:16:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't get a better opportunity!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.58,0:17:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There, there, you're a good child.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.06,0:17:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.46,0:17:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please spare us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.29,0:17:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.86,0:17:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.56,0:17:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Woman…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.59,0:17:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.36,0:17:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you try to take away this kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.62,0:17:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes…because\Nhe was crying alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.39,0:17:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do me a favor…\Ntake this kid and…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.87,0:17:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You again?\NSoul Reaper's dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.23,0:17:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.62,0:17:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will kill our enemies!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.26,0:17:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got you now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.46,0:18:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Fancy meeting you here!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.25,0:18:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.27,0:18:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take that kid and\Nget away from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.37,0:18:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.18,0:18:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.01,0:18:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.66,0:18:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.82,0:19:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for this…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.70,0:19:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.14,0:19:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't settle this until\NI attacked head-on…right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.50,0:19:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.02,0:19:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm here…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.67,0:19:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.20,0:19:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– Reap…\N– Reap…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.98,0:19:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go to sleep,\Ngo to sleep little darling…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.61,0:19:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go to sleep, go to sleep{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.30,0:19:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're a good child…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.70,0:19:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go to sleep…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.54,0:19:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One question:\NWhat'd you do with the kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.39,0:19:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what\Nyou're talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.22,0:20:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why don't we put an end\Nto this right about now…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.94,0:20:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, good idea…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.30,0:20:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We get along don't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.12,0:20:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.94,0:20:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't…cry…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.90,0:20:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey…Am I going to turn back\Nto being a normal Zanpakuto?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.82,0:21:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.54,0:21:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I'm a Zanpakuto again…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.02,0:21:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What will you and I fight for?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.82,0:21:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll fight to protect something…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.54,0:21:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.88,0:21:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't stand words\Nfrom a hypocrite?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.18,0:21:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.58,0:21:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.03,0:21:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I don't have a choice…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.06,0:21:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't cry…huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.15,0:23:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Wabisuke, who was that kid\NKazeshini was carrying around?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.55,0:23:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wouldn't return home…\Nand he had a baby…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.98,0:23:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's only one conclusion we\Ncan draw from those two things…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.53,0:23:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.12,0:23:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was his love child.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.42,0:23:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.20,0:23:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Illustrated Guide to Soul Reapers!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.03,0:23:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.06,0:23:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't much,\Nbut I wanted you to have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.03,0:23:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.48,0:23:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I caused you\Na great deal of trouble
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.57,0:23:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when I was under\NMuramasa's mind control…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.53,0:23:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a small token of apology.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.57,0:23:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that isn't necessary…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.81,0:23:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're very kind, Sir Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.47,0:23:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking forward to working\Nwith you from now on!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.87,0:23:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.80,0:24:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. If you'll excuse me…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.56,0:24:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I caused you so much\Ntrouble in the past…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.39,0:24:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's like a totally\Ndifferent person now…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.09,0:24:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,